{"tid":1212881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】有咩方法可以馬上令速龍失去活動能力？","createTime":"2019-06-12T23:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T00:23:37.000Z","uid":232082,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc49447a6fe6dc0aa5824ffb6fb09aab02907f5","tid":1212881,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:12:34.000Z","msg":"夢見一堆速龍 佢地無理無故無定向胡亂攻擊啲村民<br />\n我覺得呢個好重要 <br />\n本人當然想所有<span style=\"color: red;\">速龍</span> 仲有佢地既<span style=\"color: red;\">家人全部慘死</span> （雖然係咪都會自然發生）<br />\n不過要理智啲 以令佢地無法移動為先<br />\n<br />\n利申：發夢去左侏羅紀公園 嚇死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d24ef3bed3f8a87acdf5b38002625410387e28","tid":1212881,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657b53bd4f5c9831a074fc2b252a1d0938fbde0c","tid":1212881,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6700285e83ef39e9658b8a7de5266c4e03dd3692","tid":1212881,"uid":68620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:16:42.000Z","msg":"其實一定要攻擊返對方先有效，<br />\n一係就美國隊長身手咁好打"},{"pid":"f1e9320b461b690d7c8362ff81145a7050c2d749","tid":1212881,"uid":203405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T23:17:43.000Z","msg":"冇裝備"},{"pi